dct_title_s: The Isle of France, or, Mauritius
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures; depths shown by soundings. "Published according to Act of Parliament 1st May 1813 by Capt. Hurd R.N., hydrographer to the Admiralty. Corrected to 1836. 1861." "711." Historic Maps copy has annotations in ms.
